name: Titled Goose Game
description:
This is a student project, a clone version of Untitled Goose Game made by Mouse Mouse.

Controls:

Move - Mouse Left Click.

Space - Honk.

Run - Left Shift.

Grab - Right Click.

Crouch - Q.

Zoom in / out - Z / X.

Wings Flap - E.

View To-Do List - Tab.

Thanks House House Studio of bringing this amazing game to us. A lot of respect to them!

Programmers: Zitta Cheng, Justin Vo；

Art Directors: Lingyan Jiang, Raveena Panja；
